assessmentQuestionVersion.questionText: Employee will perform services for [Company Name] that may require [Company Name] to disclose confidential and proprietary information ("Confidential Information") to Employee. (Confidential Information is information and data of any kind concerning any matters affecting or relating to [Company Name], the business or operations of [Company Name], and/or the products, drawings, plans, processes, or other data of [Company Name] not generally known or available outside of the company.)
